messages.msgSnippet: Items such as journals, stationary, state t shirts, games, puzzles, windchimes, posters...we can set up just about any swap.  I have a place in the database
messages.messageBody:
Items such as journals, stationary, state t shirts, games, puzzles,
windchimes, posters...we can set up just about any swap. I have a
place in the database for people to list items they would like to see
as swaps. I also have a pen pal list for kids, secret sister,
birthday swap. I belong to another group like this and it is so much
fun.

Denise
